      <akn:section eId="sec_38_2910">
        <akn:num>38-2910</akn:num>
        <akn:heading>Procedure for adjusting appropriation in case of revenue unavailability.</akn:heading>
<akn:subsection eId="subsec_38-2910_1">
      <akn:num>(1)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p>The Council shall reduce the foundation level accordingly, and set a schedule for achieving or restoring full funding, however, funding shall not be less than 95% of the previous fiscal yearâ€™s funding; and</akn:p></akn:content>
    </akn:subsection><akn:subsection eId="subsec_38-2910_2">
      <akn:num>(2)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p>The Mayor, Council, Superintendent/CEO, and Board of Education shall use their best efforts to obtain temporary supplemental funding from other revenue sources.</akn:p></akn:content>
    </akn:subsection>
